dct_title_s: Automobile road from Los Angeles, Cal. to Phoenix, Ariz. via San Bernardino - Brawley - Yuma - Phoeonix
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways.
Indicates distances from Los Angeles and Phoenix.
Numbered 185 at lower right, 2 at upper right, and 61 in left margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
